    "steam_appid": 3318640,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Your business is finished.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Let's get out of here as soon as possible.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Company rules</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>No running</strong> in the office</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Follow the rules</strong> of the road</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >At ○○, <strong>don't turn around</strong> and go straight ahead.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Punish those who do not follow the rules.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game Description</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game is a short walking simulator.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Walk through the company and head for the exit.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >That is the only objective.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Something may happen along the way, but don't worry about it.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u>As long as you follow the rules.</u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >【Playing time】</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >About <strong>10 to 30 minutes.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you want to collect all endings, it will take <strong>about 1  to 2 hour</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >【Operation Methods】</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >WASD, arrow keys: Move</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >WASD key, arrow keys + Shift key: Run</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >E key: Interact</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Tab key: Open/close inventory</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Arrow keys: Switch items in inventory</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Esc key: Show/hide menu screen</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Operation instructions are also provided in the game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >【Rules for Live Streaming and Distribution】</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Anyone is welcome to play and stream the game (no permission is required).</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Monetization through distribution is also acceptable for both corporations and individuals.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >We would appreciate it if you include the name of the game in the title of the video or streaming video, and a link to the Steam store page in the summary section.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Posting or live distribution of content that is offensive to public order and morals or that significantly damages the value of the game is prohibited.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >We will not be held responsible for any damages incurred by the publisher or any third party as a result of posting or live distribution of videos.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The above terms and conditions are subject to change without notice.</p></li></ul>",
